Date: 0/0/1970
Source: Nomenclature of NZ Fish
Author: SORENSON
Vol / Page: 15
Edition:
Quote: <i>COD, BLUE</i> (a) Scientific name: <i>Parapercis colias</i>. (b) Suggested commercial name[s]: Blue cod; New Zealand cod. (c) Other common names: Coal fish (first applied by Captain Cook). (d) Principal localities where taken: ... abundant only about south of Cook Strait and at Chatham Islands.
